---
// Pillars section - Fully Translucent for Background Flow
---

<section class="pillars" id="pillars">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">The Three Pillars of My Blog</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Exploring the intersection of the soil, the system, and the soul.
    </p>

    <div class="pillars-grid">
      <div class="pillar-card earth">
        <div class="pillar-header">
          <div class="pillar-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M11 20A7 7 0 0 1 9.8 6.1C15.5 5 17 4.5 21 2c-2 5-2.5 7-2.5 10"></path>
              <path d="M12 20v-4"></path>
              <path d="M7 20h10"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="pillar-title">The Earth</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Sustainable living in Aotearoa. Gardening, fruit trees, and community support.</p>
        <div class="tag-list">
          <span class="tag">Gardening</span>
          <span class="tag">Horticulture</span>
          <span class="tag">Support Worker</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card wire">
        <div class="pillar-header">
          <div class="pillar-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
              <rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
              <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6" y2="6"></line>
              <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="pillar-title">The Wire</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Digital sovereignty. Linux distributions, self-hosting, and home lab documentation.</p>
        <div class="tag-list">
          <span class="tag">Linux</span>
          <span class="tag">HomeLab</span>
          <span class="tag">Self-Hosting</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pillar-card mind">
        <div class="pillar-header">
          <div class="pillar-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 3a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-4.5 4.5c0 4.5 4.5 10.5 4.5 10.5s4.5-6 4.5-10.5A4.5 4.5 0 0 0 12 3z"></path>
              <circle cx="12" cy="7.5" r="1.5"></circle>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="pillar-title">The Mind & Machine</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="pillar-desc">Understanding the world. Spiritual philosophy, BAPS practice, and psychology.</p>
        <div class="tag-list">
          <span class="tag">Yoga</span>
          <span class="tag">Philosophy</span>
          <span class="tag">Sanatan</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="library-footer">
      <a href="https://desi.kiwi" target="_blank" class="library-btn">
        <span>Visit desi.kiwi </span>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pillars {
    padding: 8rem 2rem;
    background: transparent; /* Essential: No background color here */
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
  
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .pillars-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .pillar-card {
    /* Glass Effect: High transparency + Backdrop Blur */
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02); 
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .pillar-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .pillar-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .pillar-icon { color: var(--color-primary); }
  .pillar-title { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; }
  .pillar-desc { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2rem; }

  .tag-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    border-radius: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .library-footer { margin-top: 5rem; text-align: center; }
  .library-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    transition: 0.3s;
  }
  
  .library-btn:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pillars { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }
    .pillar-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>